    <field name="abstract_teim">Charles Solomon was a socialist, a New York State Assemblyman, and a New York City magistrate. Contains correspondence, legal papers relating to matters brought before Solomon as magistrate, manuscripts, clippings and scrapbooks.</field>
    <field name="abstract_ssm">Charles Solomon was a socialist, a New York State Assemblyman, and a New York City magistrate. Contains correspondence, legal papers relating to matters brought before Solomon as magistrate, manuscripts, clippings and scrapbooks.</field>
    <field name="unitdate_normal_ssm">1916/1965</field>
    <field name="unitdate_normal_teim">1916/1965</field>
